{"tid":135282,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"廣東話正字","createTime":"2017-02-26T08:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T10:19:35.000Z","uid":53682,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"97f02a82ed3ebbe59d82750c5fbdea7560a97f4b","tid":135282,"uid":53682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T08:45:53.000Z","msg":"之前有唔少巴打講咗「嗰」、「喺」、「嚟」等用字，今次我想講啲比較少見嘅。 <br />\n<br />\n1. 天氣咁凍，皮膚乾裂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正解：「㿺㿭」（可讀作：爆拆）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 我真係「等」你開心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正解：戥（可讀作：鄧）<br />\n<br />\n戥有「為」、「替」嘅意思。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 想串人講嘢唔流利？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正解：㪐㩿（可讀作：甩咳） <br />\n<br />\n4. 天氣咁凍，最好食一碗「熱辣辣」嘅粥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正解： 㶧（Nad）與辣（Lad）讀音唔相同。前者有鼻音。<br />\n而且只有㶧先有「熱」嘅意思。<br />\n<br />\n5. 呢碗豆腐花真係「滑溜溜」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正解：滑捋捋（可讀作：劣）<br />\n<br />\n6. 你唔好再「Un」腳啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正解：䟴有「振動」嘅意思。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff400777d657189dd5d693357dcb17c0b7139279","tid":135282,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T08:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192da055ac284d5db6f3fcd142a72977014c39ee","tid":135282,"uid":18706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T08:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fadbe7b782cb5ea029f28b0b1fb866981b4387c","tid":135282,"uid":57636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T08:52:18.000Z","msg":"以前好鍾意睇最緊要正字<br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc52d61bbf0c004b9cc8b41e762d5a399bb00730","tid":135282,"uid":53682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T08:59:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前好鍾意睇最緊要正字<br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"326c8d2fb8a4a1dd59bf3852a0031d1f60873d14","tid":135282,"uid":6786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T09:10:06.000Z","msg":"摩牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbec7f03b71e6a4c4eaf517e53a9c6d60892550e","tid":135282,"uid":5399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T09:11:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29dde8855880389b03a199bff194e37756a6a92c","tid":135282,"uid":48729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T09:24:44.000Z","msg":"見到咁好人鍾意廣東話，我覺得係好事。<br />\n不過我有責任提醒大家，坊間你見到好多講「正字」嘅書，一般都錯漏百出。但係邊啲係真邊啲係假，一般人好判斷。有啲甚至我哋已經確認咗偽說源頭，但係仲有勁多人用。<br />\n<br />\n大家用正常人睇得明嘅寫法寫嘢就得，唔好太執着正字。<br />\n<br />\n利申：《粵典》總編輯"},{"pid":"567821d7e24fada08f02c7f4c1c0c0b942a77a84","tid":135282,"uid":53682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T09:38:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到咁好人鍾意廣東話，我覺得係好事。<br />\n不過我有責任提醒大家，坊間你見到好多講「正字」嘅書，一般都錯漏百出。但係邊啲係真邊啲係假，一般人好判斷。有啲甚至我哋已經確認咗偽說源頭，但係仲有勁多人用。<br />\n<br />\n大家用正常人睇得明嘅寫法寫嘢就得，唔好太執着正字。<br />\n<br />\n利申：《粵典》總編輯</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d4306afcea2ddb002f28ae8a23a4d88132fba1","tid":135282,"uid":53682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T09:39:13.000Z","msg":"繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n7. 你帶我去埋呢啲「山卡啦」嘅地方想點呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正解：山旮旯 （可讀作：Ca乸)<br />\n<br />\n旮旯有「偏僻」嘅意思。<br />\n<br />\n8. 你可以咁成功都係「父碌」㗎咋！（靠父親忙碌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n正解：符籙<br />\n意思係指誤打誤撞之下，又畀佢成功咗！<br />\n呢個係有啲意思，「符」即係帝王專用嘅令符，「籙」即係道教入面紀錄天神嘅名冊。簡單嚟講，「符籙」就即係帝王指令班天神去做任務。<br />\n（所以你哋符籙嘅時候，都要多謝帝王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n9. 想撩人「咬手瓜」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正解：拗手膼<br />\n「膼」即係二頭肌（老鼠仔）"},{"pid":"5a871416ca2060d4778630023760bf7fa563f0af","tid":135282,"uid":48729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T09:47:44.000Z","msg":"負碌（fluke）係篤波、運動術語，<br />\n符籙 信一成都失明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c1aef3dcfc60c1bf36699a8d3a4b359af8b497","tid":135282,"uid":53682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T09:52:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>負碌（fluke）係篤波、運動術語，<br />\n符籙 信一成都失明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇嚟我都係返去讀多啲書先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad9cfbce149b76f2c0037572e556e4e9ecfda28","tid":135282,"uid":572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T09:57:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>負碌（fluke）係篤波、運動術語，<br />\n符籙 信一成都失明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇嚟我都係返去讀多啲書先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d02aae13151eb1cca5683b01bfeeb9bb3c6988","tid":135282,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T10:01:32.000Z","msg":"fluke啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8da6ab31eed0da3a9b275a45aa8bce9c7f39abd","tid":135282,"uid":48729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T10:02:42.000Z","msg":"（提提大家，二十世紀初嘅詹憲慈、孔仲南，近年嘅曾焯文、彭志銘，都可以blacklist）"},{"pid":"d47428cc301ce58dd1b02d5eadb0b818d64e07bb","tid":135282,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T10:03:58.000Z","msg":"比 vs 畀"},{"pid":"f929914a70ff8141642f482b26901d4d413b5aa7","tid":135282,"uid":54812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T10:19:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到咁好人鍾意廣東話，我覺得係好事。<br />\n不過我有責任提醒大家，坊間你見到好多講「正字」嘅書，一般都錯漏百出。但係邊啲係真邊啲係假，一般人好判斷。有啲甚至我哋已經確認咗偽說源頭，但係仲有勁多人用。<br />\n<br />\n大家用正常人睇得明嘅寫法寫嘢就得，唔好太執着正字。<br />\n<br />\n利申：《粵典》總編輯</blockquote><br />\n爸打之前係唔係有出post教人廣東話定唔知其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}